article_title: Who Benefits Most From Repealing The Obamacare Cadillac Tax?

article_metadata.description: Despite dramatic claims of the critics of the Cadillac tax, repeal would do little to benefit low-income households and on average help middle-income taxpayers only modestly.
article_metadata.author: Business in the Beltway
